1
00:00:06,150 --> 00:00:09,420
♪By the small window♪

2
00:00:10,070 --> 00:00:13,260
♪She is grooming herself♪

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:19,860
♪A fleeting dream at night
brings me back home♪

4
00:00:20,100 --> 00:00:22,180
♪The setting sun glows on the willows♪

5
00:00:22,300 --> 00:00:23,980
♪On the quiet walls♪

6
00:00:24,140 --> 00:00:26,900
♪Only a few words are left♪

7
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:33,500
♪In my twilight years,
I long for what is lost♪

8
00:00:33,540 --> 00:00:36,420
♪I do not try to remember♪

9
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:40,620
♪How far we were apart♪

10
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:47,620
♪But forgetting is hard, with nowhere
to talk my cold thoughts out♪

11
00:00:47,860 --> 00:00:54,740
♪We looked at each other, silent,
lines of tears coursing down♪

12
00:00:54,860 --> 00:00:59,100
♪Now I gaze at the full moon all alone,
lost in its melancholic beauty♪

13
00:00:59,100 --> 00:01:02,980
[Agarwood Like a Dream]

14
00:01:03,140 --> 00:01:07,180
[Episode 4]

15
00:01:07,180 --> 00:01:09,270
[Pleasure House]

16
00:01:10,940 --> 00:01:13,540
Come, sir.

17
00:01:13,660 --> 00:01:15,580
It's been a while, Mr. Nan Qing.

18
00:01:15,580 --> 00:01:17,340
Did you miss us?

19
00:01:17,340 --> 00:01:18,020
Let's go.

20
00:01:26,980 --> 00:01:27,660
Move.

21
00:01:29,580 --> 00:01:30,260
Stop.

22
00:01:35,460 --> 00:01:38,860
Clean yourself up
and get ready for guests.

23
00:01:41,540 --> 00:01:44,260
I'm Ms. Chen,
the Ye family master's wife.

24
00:01:44,460 --> 00:01:46,660
Let me go and you won't regret it.

25
00:01:47,380 --> 00:01:48,820
Shameless.

26
00:01:49,460 --> 00:01:51,740
I've only heard of a Lady Bai
at the Ye's Mansion.

27
00:01:51,740 --> 00:01:54,060
I've never heard of a Lady Chen.

28
00:01:54,060 --> 00:01:56,140
Bai Anyuan and I are both Ye's wives.

29
00:01:56,140 --> 00:01:57,060
We married him at the same banquet

30
00:01:57,060 --> 00:01:57,700
on the same day.

31
00:01:57,700 --> 00:01:58,740
How would you not know?

32
00:01:59,100 --> 00:02:00,020
Okay.

33
00:02:00,380 --> 00:02:02,180
I'll shut the store today

34
00:02:02,300 --> 00:02:03,260
just to give you a lesson,

35
00:02:03,260 --> 00:02:05,380
you shameless wretch.

36
00:02:05,740 --> 00:02:06,540
Let me go.

37
00:02:07,220 --> 00:02:08,020
Move.

38
00:02:36,660 --> 00:02:37,980
Who came in here?

39
00:02:39,380 --> 00:02:41,260
It was Meng's mother.

40
00:02:41,540 --> 00:02:43,220
No, not me!

41
00:02:43,220 --> 00:02:44,540
Mother!

42
00:02:44,540 --> 00:02:46,220
Beat her until she admits it.

43
00:02:46,660 --> 00:02:48,620
Mother, don't go!

44
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:53,180
Meng!

45
00:03:02,020 --> 00:03:03,420
Buhan, did you have a nightmare?

46
00:03:03,820 --> 00:03:04,820
Why are you here?

47
00:03:06,340 --> 00:03:08,340
I came to see if you were sleeping well.

48
00:03:08,340 --> 00:03:09,300
Should I not come?

49
00:03:10,020 --> 00:03:10,820
Buheng!

50
00:03:13,420 --> 00:03:14,140
Mr. Ye.

51
00:03:14,820 --> 00:03:15,620
Escort her back.

52
00:03:17,620 --> 00:03:18,660
No need.

53
00:03:19,660 --> 00:03:20,980
Now that you don't wish to,

54
00:03:22,380 --> 00:03:23,980
I'll leave by myself.

55
00:03:28,900 --> 00:03:30,460
How come you had nightmares again?

56
00:03:31,100 --> 00:03:31,900
Buheng,

57
00:03:32,620 --> 00:03:33,420
did Ying Hemeng

58
00:03:33,980 --> 00:03:35,380
really die in Suiyang?

59
00:03:38,700 --> 00:03:40,860
Since you've accepted the gold sycee,

60
00:03:41,380 --> 00:03:42,820
she is mine.

61
00:03:42,820 --> 00:03:43,900
Of course.

62
00:03:44,260 --> 00:03:45,380
She is awake.

63
00:03:45,460 --> 00:03:48,780
I won't disturb you any longer.

64
00:03:49,660 --> 00:03:50,460
Go.

65
00:04:09,300 --> 00:04:10,980
Rumeng, you're awake.

66
00:04:10,980 --> 00:04:11,780
Who are you?

67
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:13,500
I'm Nan Qing.

68
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:15,580
At the incense competition
at the Ye's Mansion,

69
00:04:15,660 --> 00:04:17,140
your butterfly-attracting incense

70
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:20,380
was quite impressive.

71
00:04:23,260 --> 00:04:24,060
Come on.

72
00:04:25,740 --> 00:04:27,020
As a guest of the Ye family,

73
00:04:27,020 --> 00:04:28,060
you must know my identity.

74
00:04:28,300 --> 00:04:29,420
How dare you be rude?

75
00:04:30,900 --> 00:04:31,900
You've misunderstood.

76
00:04:32,900 --> 00:04:34,540
I'm here to apply medicine for you.

77
00:04:46,780 --> 00:04:48,260
They were too harsh with you.

78
00:04:48,900 --> 00:04:50,420
The Ye family
isn't looking after you either.

79
00:04:51,700 --> 00:04:52,620
Mr. Nan Qing.

80
00:04:54,340 --> 00:04:57,300
I am Ye's wife.

81
00:05:02,900 --> 00:05:05,020
Swollen wrists
may seem like a small injury.

82
00:05:05,220 --> 00:05:06,900
If not treated in time,

83
00:05:06,900 --> 00:05:08,220
they could lead to chronic issues.

84
00:05:12,900 --> 00:05:15,180
Why is this entirely different

85
00:05:15,180 --> 00:05:16,340
from Butterflies Dancing Among Flowers?

86
00:05:17,740 --> 00:05:20,700
The incense makers followed
the formula you provided.

87
00:05:21,220 --> 00:05:22,300
They've tried for a few days

88
00:05:22,540 --> 00:05:23,860
but failed to achieve the effect.

89
00:05:25,340 --> 00:05:26,140
Perhaps,

90
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:29,700
Ms. Chen hasn't included all the steps

91
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:31,380
in the formula.

92
00:05:32,220 --> 00:05:33,980
Since when did you know incense making?

93
00:05:37,260 --> 00:05:39,820
Bad news. Ms. Chen is missing.

94
00:05:45,980 --> 00:05:47,500
Master has sent word.

95
00:05:49,020 --> 00:05:51,740
They'll send people
to take her to the Pleasure House.

96
00:06:14,820 --> 00:06:15,620
Mr. Ye,

97
00:06:15,980 --> 00:06:18,020
I've questioned the side gate guard.

98
00:06:18,420 --> 00:06:20,900
I'm afraid Ms. Chen was sold
to the Pleasure House.

99
00:06:24,980 --> 00:06:25,940
I'm here to see the master.

100
00:06:26,100 --> 00:06:26,980
Master is away,

101
00:06:27,060 --> 00:06:28,420
but I was told

102
00:06:28,420 --> 00:06:29,260
to ask you to go back.

103
00:06:29,620 --> 00:06:31,140
Master sent word the other day,

104
00:06:31,140 --> 00:06:32,300
telling me not to worry

105
00:06:32,340 --> 00:06:34,420
and that you would take Chen Rumeng
out of the Ye family.

106
00:06:34,460 --> 00:06:36,740
But now Buhan knows
she's been sold to the Pleasure House

107
00:06:36,740 --> 00:06:37,620
and has rushed there to save her.

108
00:06:37,660 --> 00:06:39,180
If he really brings her back,

109
00:06:39,220 --> 00:06:41,220
how can I stay in the Ye family?

110
00:06:41,260 --> 00:06:42,660
How can Master just sit and watch?

111
00:06:42,860 --> 00:06:46,140
Lady, the Ye family
is nothing but a shell now.

112
00:06:46,300 --> 00:06:49,340
The Qixiang Pavilion doesn't lack
women who can make incense.

113
00:06:49,340 --> 00:06:51,660
They need money
to address their urgent needs.

114
00:06:51,860 --> 00:06:53,260
Master has asked me

115
00:06:53,260 --> 00:06:55,340
to gather several carts
of silver and precious ingredients,

116
00:06:55,460 --> 00:06:57,260
which will be sent
to the Ye's Mansion soon.

117
00:06:57,340 --> 00:06:59,700
The Ye family will also treat you
with the most respect.

118
00:07:00,460 --> 00:07:02,500
Please do not worry.

119
00:07:20,580 --> 00:07:22,140
It was inconvenient to initiate a chat

120
00:07:22,220 --> 00:07:23,140
at the incense competition.

121
00:07:23,700 --> 00:07:26,660
I couldn't express
my admiration for you.

122
00:07:27,140 --> 00:07:27,940
Actually,

123
00:07:28,700 --> 00:07:29,660
I believe

124
00:07:29,660 --> 00:07:32,340
the sense of smell is the closest
to connecting with one's spirit.

125
00:07:32,740 --> 00:07:36,020
Your incense struck me strongly.

126
00:07:37,140 --> 00:07:40,380
I didn't know you also thought
smell could reach one's spirit.

127
00:07:40,540 --> 00:07:41,340
I do.

128
00:07:42,020 --> 00:07:43,500
Only incense makers know

129
00:07:43,620 --> 00:07:45,420
be it incense seals,

130
00:07:45,740 --> 00:07:46,660
incense sticks,

131
00:07:46,660 --> 00:07:47,700
or charcoal-heated incense,

132
00:07:47,860 --> 00:07:51,060
even with the same formula
and ingredients,

133
00:07:51,140 --> 00:07:53,620
different weather,
temperatures, and distances

134
00:07:53,740 --> 00:07:55,500
can lead to different scents.

135
00:07:55,740 --> 00:07:56,700
A scent is like...

136
00:07:58,460 --> 00:08:00,100
a dish your mother made
when you were a child.

137
00:08:00,620 --> 00:08:03,300
If someone can replicate that taste,

138
00:08:03,740 --> 00:08:06,340
you'll recall your childhood
and your mother,

139
00:08:06,340 --> 00:08:07,260
right?

140
00:08:07,540 --> 00:08:08,820
Among all the senses,

141
00:08:09,020 --> 00:08:12,660
smell carries the longest memories.

142
00:08:13,500 --> 00:08:15,980
Sir, you truly understand incense.

143
00:08:16,820 --> 00:08:17,540
I'm flattered.

144
00:08:56,060 --> 00:08:57,900
It's a great pleasure

145
00:08:58,020 --> 00:08:59,100
knowing you.

146
00:08:59,180 --> 00:09:02,300
But it's time for me
to return to the Ye's Mansion.

147
00:09:03,940 --> 00:09:05,620
Since you live in the Ye's Mansion,

148
00:09:05,620 --> 00:09:07,420
it will be difficult

149
00:09:07,620 --> 00:09:08,660
to talk with you like this.

150
00:09:10,340 --> 00:09:12,860
I've heard Mr. Ye has quite the temper.

151
00:09:13,220 --> 00:09:14,020
In recent years,

152
00:09:14,020 --> 00:09:16,420
he's only let a few incense makers
stay at the Qixiang Pavilion.

153
00:09:16,660 --> 00:09:18,180
Perhaps the incense
from the Qixiang Pavilion

154
00:09:18,420 --> 00:09:20,020
isn't as good as it used to be.

155
00:09:21,100 --> 00:09:22,420
I remember ten years ago

156
00:09:22,620 --> 00:09:24,500
when I first smelled Night Spirit
from the Qixiang Pavilion.

157
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:26,020
- It was refreshing and elegant.
- It's what Mother made.

158
00:09:26,020 --> 00:09:27,220
It impressed me.

159
00:09:28,020 --> 00:09:29,340
You like Night Spirit too?

160
00:09:29,820 --> 00:09:31,380
Yes, you know...

161
00:09:37,700 --> 00:09:38,500
Mr. Ye.

162
00:09:45,050 --> 00:09:48,800
[Bai's Mansion]

163
00:09:49,380 --> 00:09:50,100
Jinling,

164
00:09:50,620 --> 00:09:52,820
remember, I've never left
the Ye's Mansion today.

165
00:09:52,940 --> 00:09:54,220
Don't worry, my lady.

166
00:09:54,340 --> 00:09:57,020
We just need to hurry back
to the Ye's Mansion

167
00:09:57,420 --> 00:09:59,220
and pretend nothing happened.

168
00:10:00,460 --> 00:10:02,940
My feelings for Buhan are sincere.

169
00:10:03,260 --> 00:10:04,660
But if I'm buying this relationship,

170
00:10:05,260 --> 00:10:06,260
what meaning will that hold?

171
00:10:06,860 --> 00:10:07,900
Please don't worry.

172
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:10,420
Mr. Ye has known you for years.

173
00:10:10,700 --> 00:10:13,620
He's just bewitched
by that woman for now.

174
00:10:13,900 --> 00:10:15,300
That wretch

175
00:10:15,300 --> 00:10:17,020
has spent a night at the Pleasure House.

176
00:10:17,340 --> 00:10:19,340
What could she be
other than a prostitute?

177
00:10:21,620 --> 00:10:24,060
Yes, she's stayed the night
at the Pleasure House.

178
00:10:24,940 --> 00:10:26,540
Even if Buhan saves her,

179
00:10:27,020 --> 00:10:28,500
the Ye family won't accept her.

180
00:10:29,060 --> 00:10:29,700
Mm-hmm.

181
00:10:38,460 --> 00:10:41,500
Buhan, I was just discussing
incense formulas with Mr. Nan Qing,

182
00:10:41,740 --> 00:10:43,020
and we shared some thoughts.

183
00:10:45,060 --> 00:10:46,660
You were talking the whole night?

184
00:10:50,340 --> 00:10:51,500
Mr. Ye, please don't misunderstand.

185
00:10:52,460 --> 00:10:54,460
But I must say

186
00:10:54,900 --> 00:10:56,340
Rumeng's formula

187
00:10:56,620 --> 00:10:58,620
shares a striking similarity
to that of Night Spirit.

188
00:10:58,660 --> 00:11:02,020
She also resembles that incense maker.

189
00:11:04,620 --> 00:11:05,420
What did you say?

190
00:11:05,740 --> 00:11:06,700
You met Ying Ling?

191
00:11:07,260 --> 00:11:09,980
Just do what I do.

192
00:11:16,860 --> 00:11:17,660
Rumeng!

193
00:11:19,740 --> 00:11:20,540
Are you okay?

194
00:11:27,220 --> 00:11:28,980
Next time, remember,

195
00:11:29,900 --> 00:11:31,980
you now have a home in Shangjing.

196
00:11:32,900 --> 00:11:34,460
Don't forget to come back home.

197
00:11:36,020 --> 00:11:37,660
Buhan, this is Meng.

198
00:11:37,660 --> 00:11:38,980
You two can play together.

199
00:11:39,540 --> 00:11:40,620
♪Familiar yet strange scenes♪

200
00:11:40,620 --> 00:11:42,380
Meng, follow me.

201
00:11:42,380 --> 00:11:43,700
This is your home.

202
00:11:43,700 --> 00:11:45,300
♪Are the origin of the story♪

203
00:11:45,620 --> 00:11:47,900
♪Growing with time♪

204
00:11:47,900 --> 00:11:51,220
♪Is somber grief♪

205
00:11:51,460 --> 00:11:54,300
♪The swan song of bait♪

206
00:11:54,780 --> 00:11:57,620
♪Has freed the heart from desires♪

207
00:11:57,900 --> 00:12:03,020
♪Love is buried deep
while I dance with the wolf♪

208
00:12:04,460 --> 00:12:09,580
♪The scented sachet haunts my dream♪

209
00:12:09,740 --> 00:12:15,660
♪Our love blazes hot with time goes by♪

210
00:12:15,780 --> 00:12:18,660
♪The lingering sorrow
as we pass each other♪

