♪The scented sachet haunts my dream♪

219
00:13:00,260 --> 00:13:04,700
♪Our love blazes hot with time goes by♪

220
00:13:05,980 --> 00:13:08,860
♪The lingering sorrow
as we pass each other♪

221
00:13:09,460 --> 00:13:12,260
♪Stings my heart♪

222
00:13:12,900 --> 00:13:17,300
♪The anguish,
how difficult it is to decipher love♪

223
00:13:19,180 --> 00:13:21,660
♪How could I withstand
the soulful gaze?♪

224
